'''Martin Yves Expérience''' (born 9 March 1999) is a professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[left-back]] for French {{French football updater|Nancy}} club [[AS Nancy Lorraine|Nancy]]. Born in France, he plays for the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]].

==Club career==
A youth product of [[Xerez CD|Xerez]], Expérience began his senior career with [[US Changé|Changé]] in 2018. After a couple of seasons there, he moved to [[US Avranches|Avranches]] in 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://saint-lo.maville.com/actu/actudet_-us-avranches.-martin-experience-a-l-heure-de-la-renaissance_fil-4252324_actu.Htm|title=US Avranches. Martin Expérience, à l'heure de la renaissance|website=saint-lo.maville.com}}</ref> In June 2022, he signed with [[SO Cholet|Cholet]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Cholet|url=https://www.socholet.fr/actualites/martin-experience-avranches-signe-a-cholet/|title=MARTIN EXPÉRIENCE (AVRANCHES) SIGNE À CHOLET|access-date=13 July 2022|language=fr}}</ref>

On 31 May 2024, Expérience joined Championnat National club [[AS Nancy Lorraine|Nancy]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.asnl.net/58/actualites/actualites/fiche/29899|trans-title=Martin Expérience joins AS Nancy-Lorraine 🖋️🔴⚪️|title=Martin Expérience rejoint l'AS Nancy-Lorraine 🖋️🔴⚪️|language=French|website=www.asnl.net|date=31 May 2024|accessdate=1 June 2024}}</ref>

==International career==
Expérience debuted with the [[Haiti national football team|Haiti national team]] in a 6–1 [[2021 CONCACAF Gold Cup qualification]] win over [[Saint Vincent and the Grenadines national football team|Saint Vincent and the Grenadines]] on 2 July 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.concacaf.com/en/gold-cup/game-details?matchid=568629|title=Game Details|date=11 March 2021|website=Gold Cup}}</ref>

